column5: Southern Living Dinner in a Dish
column10:
• This hefty, 344 page book organizes top-rated Southern Living recipes into hundreds of quick and easy dinnertime solutions

  • All 200 recipes in the book are easy one-recipe meals for casseroles, slow-cookers, skillet suppers, stir-fry, pizza and pasta, soup and salad, meals from the grill, and more

  • Over 100 full-color photographs help readers easily identify family-favorite recipes

  • This hefty, 344 page book organizes top-rated Southern Living recipes into hundreds of quick and easy dinnertime solutions

  • Over 100 full-color photographs help readers easily identify family-favorite recipes

  • Hundreds of hints, tips, and shortcut secrets are shared by the Southern Living Test Kitchen experts and Shopper's Companion boxes throughout the book suggest ingredient substitutions and meal accompaniments
